$ %CommonProgramFiles%

The default location of `%CommonProgramFiles%` seems to be `C:\Program Files\Common Files`

Some subdirectories might be:
  • → Windows/dirs/Program-Files/Common-Files/microsoft-shared[`microsoft shared`]
  • → Windows/dirs/Program-Files/Common-Files/System[`System`]

sa:
  `CommonFilesDir` and `CommonW6432Dir` under the → Windows/registry[registry] key
  → Windows/registry/tree/HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/Software/Microsoft/Windows/CurrentVersion[`HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion`]

  → Windows/dirs/Program-Files-x86/Common-Files[`%CommonProgramFiles(x86)%`]

  → Windows/dirs/Program-Files[`C:\Program  Files`]
